'''瑪麗·伊麗莎白·哈夫'''<ref>中文譯名引自[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]：[http://iipdigital.usembassy.gov/st/chinese/article/2014/05/20140506298838.html#axzz3Z66erHwa 美国将加强同叙利亚反对派的关系] {{Wayback|url=http://iipdigital.usembassy.gov/st/chinese/article/2014/05/20140506298838.html#axzz3Z66erHwa |date=20150714034053 }}</ref>（{{lang-en|Marie Elizabeth Harf}}，{{bd|1981年|6月15日}}），是[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]的战略沟通资深顾问與前任副[[發言人|發言人]]，以及前任的[[中央情报局|中央情报局]]（CIA）發言人。她曾於[[2012年美國總統大選|2012年美國總統大選]]時，在[[歐巴馬|歐巴馬]]的競選團隊中工作。
==早年生活==
她是Jane Ax Harf of Granville, Ohio和James E. Harf of St. Louis.的女兒<ref>{{cite web|title=Marie Harf, Joshua Lucas — Weddings|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/15/fashion/weddings/marie-harf-joshua-lucas-weddings.html|website=http://www.nytimes.com|accessdate=April 30, 2015|date=April 15, 2012|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414222010/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/15/fashion/weddings/marie-harf-joshua-lucas-weddings.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Daily Press Briefing - Jan 15, 2015|url=http://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/dpb/2015/01/236028.htm|website=http://www.state.gov/|accessdate=March 26, 2015|date=January 15, 2015|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012220349/https://www.state.gov/r/pa/prs/dpb/2015/01/236028.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在{{link-en|格蘭維爾 (俄亥俄州)|Granville, Ohio|格蘭維爾}}長大，1999年畢業於格蘭維爾高中（Granville High School）<ref>{{cite web|title=Granville grad speaks for State Department|url=http://www.newarkadvocate.com/article/20131228/NEWS01/312280014/Granville-grad-speaks-State-Department|website=http://www.newarkadvocate.com/|accessdate=July 1, 2014|author=Drew Bracken|date=December 31, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111100216/http://www.newarkadvocate.com/article/20131228/NEWS01/312280014/Granville-grad-speaks-State-Department|archivedate=2014年11月11日}}</ref>。之後，她就讀於{{link-en|印第安那大學伯明頓分校|Indiana University Bloomington}}，取得[[政治學|政治學]]學士學位；並於[[弗吉尼亚大学|弗吉尼亚大学]]取得外交事務[[碩士|碩士]]學位<ref name="Harf on DoS">{{cite web|title=Marie Harf|url=http://www.state.gov/r/pa/ei/biog/bureau/220636.htm|website=http://www.state.gov/|accessdate=July 1, 2014|archive-date=2015-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150310132922/http://www.state.gov/r/pa/ei/biog/bureau/220636.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==職業生涯==
[[File:Marie_Elizabeth_Harf,20140725.jpg|缩略图]]
她的職業生涯起始於擔任中情局的情報分析員，主要著重在[[中東問題|中東問題]]方面，之後她成為了中情局的媒體發言人。<ref name="FP Cable"/>

[[2012年美國總統大選|2012年美國總統大選]]期間，她成為總統[[歐巴馬|歐巴馬]]競選時的團隊一員，負責協助國家與通信安全對策的政見規劃，兼任選戰時的國安問題發言人<ref name="Harf on DoS"/><ref name="FP Cable">{{cite news |author=Josh Rogin |coauthors= |title=Former Obama spokesperson moving to State |url=http://thecable.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2013/04/30/former_obama_spokesperson_moving_to_state |quote= |pages= |work=FP |location= |date=April 30, 2013 |accessdate=July 11, 2014 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714182257/http://thecable.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2013/04/30/former_obama_spokesperson_moving_to_state |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年6月，她被任命為[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]的副發言人，擔任[[珍·莎琪|珍·莎琪]]的副手<ref name="Harf on DoS"/><ref name="FP Cable"/>。

2015年6月1日，她正式晉升為[[美國國務卿|美國國務卿]][[约翰·克里|约翰·克里]]的战略沟通资深顾问（Senior Advisor for Strategic Communications）<ref>{{cite news|title=Marie Harf Promoted to Senior Advisor to John Kerry|url=http://insider.foxnews.com/2015/05/27/marie-harf-promoted-senior-advisor-john-kerry|accessdate=2015-06-01|agency=[[foxnews|foxnews]]|date=2015-05-27|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224041614/https://insider.foxnews.com/2015/05/27/marie-harf-promoted-senior-advisor-john-kerry|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年1月後，哈夫在[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]擔任[[時事評論員|政治評論員]]<ref name="adweek.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.adweek.com/tvnewser/fox-news-signs-former-state-department-spokesperson-marie-harf-as-contributor/318311|title=Fox News Signs Former State Dept. Spokesperson Marie Harf as Contributor|website=adweek.com|accessdate=August 16, 2017|archive-date=2017-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170314213201/https://www.adweek.com/tvnewser/fox-news-signs-former-state-department-spokesperson-marie-harf-as-contributor/318311|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 失言風波 ===
2015年2月，她在一個美國[[脫口秀|脫口秀]]節目『{{link-en|Hardball with Chris Matthews|Hardball with Chris Matthews}}』受訪時稱，消滅[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]的辦法就是幫他們（[[恐怖份子|恐怖份子]]）找工作，因為那裏的[[窮人|窮人]]太多了。此一說法立刻招致批評<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/02/18/yes-i-ll-say-it-marie-harf-had-a-point.html|title=-{Yes, I’ll Say It: Marie Harf Had a Point}-|author=Michael Tomasky|publisher=The Daily Beast|date=February 18, 2015|accessdate=February 19, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author1=宋凌蘭(譯)|title=「用就業解決IS問題」…國務院發言人失言挨轟|url=http://www.worldjournal.com/2247155/article-%E3%80%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BAis%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E3%80%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%99%A2%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%A8%80%E6%8C%A8%E8%BD%9F/?ref=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B|accessdate=2015-05-03|agency=[[世界新聞網|世界新聞網]]|date=2015-02-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423164932/http://www.worldjournal.com/2247155/article-%E3%80%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BAis%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E3%80%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%99%A2%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%A8%80%E6%8C%A8%E8%BD%9F/?ref=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B|archivedate=2015-04-23}}</ref>。

